Okuyasu Nijimura

203
00:14:42,390 --> 00:14:44,440
Instead of looking for a Stand to kill him,

204
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:47,960
if you'll try to find one that can cure him,

205
00:14:49,340 --> 00:14:50,860
I don't mind helping you out.

206
00:14:54,380 --> 00:14:57,080
But hand over that bow and arrow.

207
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:58,250
I'm gonna snap them in half.

208
00:15:02,900 --> 00:15:04,640
You planning to run?

209
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:09,930
Big Bro, let's stop this.

210
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:11,950
Okuyasu!

211
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:17,640
Come on, let's stop all of this, okay?

212
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:19,140
You were still here?

213
00:15:20,600 --> 00:15:23,650
Dad might get cured, right?

214
00:15:26,260 --> 00:15:29,610
Even if his body doesn't go back to normal,

215
00:15:29,610 --> 00:15:34,800
maybe his mind and his memories
will go back to how he used to be.

216
00:15:35,540 --> 00:15:36,440
Right?

217
00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:44,630
Okuyasu! What do you think you're holding?

218
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:46,130
Big Bro...

219
00:15:47,210 --> 00:15:49,060
Out of the way, Okuyasu!

220
00:15:49,060 --> 00:15:53,050
I can't turn back anymore,
no matter what happens!

221
00:15:53,050 --> 00:15:57,390
I've already killed so many people in
this city with this bow and arrow!

222
00:15:58,230 --> 00:16:02,240
Besides, I don't even think of you
as my little brother anymore.

223
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:05,900
Since you're not my little brother,
I can kill you without hesitation!

224
00:16:08,030 --> 00:16:10,020
B-Big Bro...

225
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:19,040
You guys...

226
00:16:19,040 --> 00:16:21,980
